name: Hostel Mancini Naples Shared Room
description: Sin especificar
host_about:
Ciao, I'm Margherita! I and my husband own and run a cozy Hostel in the center of Naples right across the  central railway station ( Napoli Centrale Piazza Garibaldi ) and next to local trains ( Circumvesuviana ) to reach Herculaneum, Pompeii and Sorrento where you can also take the "SITA" bus to Positano and Amalfi.

Hostel Pensione Mancini lies in a very central position, a few steps from Naples railway station, and 20 minutes bus ride from Capodichino Airport or 6 minutes ride from the Port. 

With its central position Hostel Pensione Mancini is an unbetable base for sightseeing the city of Naples and for daytrips (to Pompeii, Ercolano, Oplonti, Vesuvio, Sorrento, Amalfi, Capri, Procida, Ischia, Pozzuoli, Baia and Cuma). 

Hostel Pensione Mancini is in the eastern side of the Old City, where the buildings date back to the VII Cent. B.C. It is an example of the best of Europe's architecture; this area is considered by UNESCO as the district with the largest number of architectural styles in the world. Art and history play a great part in the eclectic and exuberant life of Neapolitans, along with the lively character of the student population; Naples University was founded in 1224 by the Gibelin Emperor Fredrick II Staufer. Small street markets, pubs, pizzerie ( MOST FAMOUS PIZZERIA DA MICHELE with only 5 min. on foot ), trattorie and discos complete the attractions of a city that will charm visitors at every step. Naples is here - come and discover it !!

Hostel Pensione Mancini is here too: come and feel at home !!!!

host_about:
In the district of Avvocata, close to the Salvator Rosa metro stop, you will find the Controra Hostel Naples. An ancient monastery that housed pilgrims today is a nice hostel, within walking distance from the chic boutiques of the Vomero.

This hostel in the centre of Naples, has a lovely garden,parking on request, and rooms with air conditioning and a balcony. You can choose to book beds in dorm rooms with shared bathroom or en suite rooms. Free wireless in public areas, games room and a reception open 24 hours a day complete the services offered.
